  "text": "achieve the best scattering results. Therefore, the bending property of microstrip is important in our proposed UWB filter design. There were several researches and studies done on microstrip bending i.e., discontinuity properties of microstrip [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . The studies were concerned on capacitance and inductance parasitic effects in microstrip circuit. As reported in [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] [CITATION_9] [CITATION_10] , the discontinuities in microstrip circuit could be modeled as a T-network. The capacitive and inductive parameter effects could be varied and compensated by cutting inner, outer or 45 • mitered at the corner of a microstrip line.",
